-- Ackman says followed the rules with Allergan investment - CNBC
-- By Caroline Humer
-- Mon Jun 09, 2014 08:21AM EDT
-- None



June 9 (Reuters) - Activist investor William Ackman said on Monday during an interview on CNBC he followed Securities and Exchange Commission rules when he invested in Allergan Inc and made a joint bid with Valeant Pharmaceuticals International Inc <VRX.TO>.

